            <head xml:id="alalal-f19249-Hd1e99">Divisio Textus</head>
            <p xml:id="alalal-f19249-d1e101">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="16"/>DIVISIO TEXTUS.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-f19249-d1e106">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="17"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-f19249-Qd1e110"> Nune de septem donis Spiritus 
san<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="18"/>cti, etc. </quote>
               <lb ed="Bd" n="19"/>Hic tertio loco inter habitus 
perficien<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="20"/>tes animam, agit Magister de donis.
</p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-f19249-d1e120">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="21"/>Et dividitur in duas partes : in quarum
<lb ed="Bd" n="22"/>prima agit de donis in communi. [n 
se<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="23"/>cunda, agit de donis in speciali, quae 
in<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="24"/>cipit in hac eadem distinclione, ibi, D,
<lb ed="Bd" n="25"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-f19249-Qd1e133"> Et quia de timore, etc. </quote>
            </p>
            <p xml:id="alalal-f19249-d1e136">
               <lb ed="Bd" n="26"/>In prima parte inquirit quatuor circa
<lb ed="Bd" n="27"/>dona in communi, quorum primum est,
<lb ed="Bd" n="28"/>an sint virtutes, et utrum sint in 
Angc<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="29"/>lis? Et haec duo determinantur simul.
<lb ed="Bd" n="30"/>Tertio, Utrum fuerunt in Christo ? ibi, B,
<lb ed="Bd" n="31"/>
               <quote xml:id="alalal-f19249-Qd1e151"> da Christo autem, etc. </quote> Quarto 
que<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="32"/>ritur, Utrum evacuabuntur vel 
remane<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="33"/>bunt in patria ? ibi, Â©, <quote xml:id="alalal-f19249-Qd1e157"> Mis autenr 
vide<lb break="no" ed="Bd" n="34"/>fur obviare, etc. </quote>
            </p>
